summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of alley in Block 7, D. S. Maynard's plat of the town (now City of Seattle, lying the alley between First S. Occidental and Washington Street in the City of Seattle, by paving under Ordinance No. 14980, creating Local Improvement District No. 1334 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
